OL,3,CRansom note about Nancy Guthrie's
OL,4,Cdisappearance claims she died
OL,6,FA ransom note linked to the
OL,7,Fdisappearance of Nancy Guthrie, the
OL,8,Fmother of American television host
OL,9,FSavannah Guthrie, said she had died,
OL,10,Faccording to investigators.
OL,12,FIt followed another ransom note that
OL,13,Fhad demanded millions of dollars, and
OL,14,Finvestigators believe the notes are
OL,15,Flegitimate communications from the
OL,16,Fkidnappers, according to ITV News' US
OL,17,Fpartner CNN.
