OL,3,CRansom note about Nancy Guthrie's
OL,4,Cdisappearance claims she died
OL,6,FThe second note said that Ms Guthrie
OL,7,Fwas dead and that the kidnappers did
OL,8,Fnot mean to kill her, but that she
OL,9,Fdied shortly after the kidnapping.
OL,11,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,12,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,13,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,14,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,16,FThe family responded with an emotional
OL,17,Fvideo on February 7 when Savannah
OL,18,FGuthrie said: "We received your
OL,19,Fmessage, and we understand."
