OL,3,CRansom note about Nancy Guthrie's
OL,4,Cdisappearance claims she died
OL,6,FBoth CNN and a local television
OL,7,Fstation in Arizona received the notes
OL,8,Fat the time.
OL,10,FThe news organisations agreed to a
OL,11,Frequest from authorities and the
OL,12,Ffamily to hold off on reporting the
OL,13,Fcontents of the notes so that any
OL,14,Ffuture communications with the
OL,15,Fkidnapper or kidnappers could be
OL,16,Fauthenticated.
