OL,3,CRansom note about Nancy Guthrie's
OL,4,Cdisappearance claims she died
OL,6,FThe Pima County Sheriff's Department,
OL,7,Fwhich has been leading the case since
OL,8,FNancy Guthrie's disappearance around
OL,9,Ffive months ago, told CNN on Monday
OL,10,Fthe investigation remains "active and
OL,11,Fongoing" and directed other questions
OL,12,Fregarding the ransom notes to the FBI.
OL,14,FMore than 20 weeks have passed since
OL,15,FMs Guthrie, 81, was reported missing
OL,16,Fon February 1, after security cameras
OL,17,Fat her Arizona home captured a masked
OL,18,Fman carrying a handgun.
