OL,3,CRansom note about Nancy Guthrie's
OL,4,Cdisappearance claims she died
OL,6,FDespite the family offering a $1
OL,7,Fmillion reward for information, there
OL,8,Fhas been little movement in the
OL,9,Finvestigation, which continues.
OL,11,FAuthorities believe she was kidnapped,
OL,12,Fabducted or otherwise taken against
OL,13,Fher will after finding blood near her
OL,14,Ffront doorstep.
