OL,3,CRansom note about Nancy Guthrie's
OL,4,Cdisappearance claims she died
OL,6,FVolunteers and search teams scoured
OL,7,Fthe nearby desert terrain, which is
OL,8,Ffilled with cacti, bushes and
OL,9,Fboulders, in the weeks after she
OL,10,Fvanished. A volunteer group recently
OL,11,Fconducted a search for her body near
OL,12,Fthe Arizona-Mexico border, but did not
OL,13,Freport having found her.
